<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/22（Sat.）Claw Machine &amp; make English its official language (Host:Ken)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=209&amp;p=223#p223"><![CDATA[
Claw Machine <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://thenextweb.com/distract/2018/06/09/taiwan-is-obsessed-with-claw-machines-and-so-am-i/">https://thenextweb.com/distract/2018/06 ... d-so-am-i/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br /> Q1.Have you ever played a claw machine? Do you know any tips to win?<br /> Q2. Have you ever won or seen interesting prizes in a claw machine? If yes, what are they? If you run a claw machine, what would you put inside to attract customers?<br /> Q3.Why are Taiwanese so obsessed with claw machines?<br /> Q4. Why have so many stores been shut down and placed with claw machines? Is the popularity good or bad for Taiwan's economy?<br /><br /><br />Topic 2: Taiwan to make English its official language <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/world/2018/08/683_254574.html">http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/world/2 ... 54574.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br /> Q1. Should we make English our secund offical language?<br /> Q2. If the policy is implemented, will it succeed?<br /> Q3. How will this change affect students, teachers, parents and English education industry?<br /> Q4. Some criticize Taiwan fails in English education. In your opinion, what is the root cause?<br />Agenda<br />7:00-7:30 free talk<br />(Session 1)<br />7:30-7:35 Opening remarks/ Newcomers self-introduction/ Grouping<br />7:35~ 8:15 discussion session (40 mins)<br />(Session 2)<br />8:15 ~9:00pm discussion session (45 mins)<br />9:00~9:30 free talk<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven, <br />板橋民生路二段237 號, <br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30, <br />minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Wed Sep 19, 2018 10:32 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
